        "pull_large_size_mobile": 24,
        "blockquote_size": 24,
        "blockquote_size_mobile": 20,
        "blockquote_border_width": 2,
        "blockquote_padding_left": 24,
        "show_editorial_placeholder": true,
        "editorial_max_width": 1020,
        "p1_lede": "UNSAID was created from the belief that the most defining parts of who we are often live in silence",
        "p1_continuation": " \u2014 the pause before a life-changing decision, the calm after internal chaos, the confidence that doesn\u2019t seek validation.",
        "p2": "In a world obsessed with noise, trends, and constant expression, we chose something different.",
        "p3_pull": "We built UNSAID for what remains unspoken.",
        "p4": "\u201cFragrance for the Unsaid\u201d is more than a tagline. It is the foundation of our brand \u2014 a reflection of emotions, identities, and moments too personal, too complex, or too profound for words.",
        "p5_prefix": "Each fragrance is designed not around gender, seasons, or fleeting trends, but around states of mind: ",
        "p5_em": "anticipation, clarity, control, unfinished emotion.",
        "p6": "Our scents are crafted to linger quietly yet powerfully \u2014 not to announce your presence, but to become part of it.",
        "p7": "UNSAID is for those who understand that true presence doesn\u2019t demand attention.",
        "p8_pull_large": "It is felt. Remembered. Recognized.",
        "p9": "We exist for individuals who wear fragrance not as decoration, but as an extension of the inner world they choose not to explain.",
        "p10_bq_line1": "Because not everything meaningful needs to be said.",
        "p10_bq_line2": "Some things are better worn."
      }
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
